OL,3,CAustralia's mushroom killer tried to
OL,4,Cpoison husband three times, court hears
OL,6,FA woman who killed three members of
OL,7,Fher estranged husband's family with a
OL,8,Fmeal laced with deadly mushrooms had
OL,9,Falso tried to poison her husband on
OL,10,Ffamily camping trips, according to
OL,11,Fcourt evidence which was made public
OL,12,Fon Friday.
OL,14,FErin Patterson was convicted last
OL,15,Fmonth of murdering her parents-in-law
OL,16,FDon and Gail Patterson, and Gail's
OL,17,Fsister Heather Wilkinson at her home
OL,18,Fin the state of Victoria with a lunch
OL,19,Fof beef Wellington containing toxic
OL,20,Fdeath cap mushrooms.
