OL,3,CAustralia's mushroom killer tried to
OL,4,Cpoison husband three times, court hears
OL,6,FShe was also found guilty of
OL,7,Fattempting to murder Ian Wilkinson,
OL,8,FHeather's husband, who survived the
OL,9,Fmeal but spent weeks recovering in
OL,10,Fhospital.
OL,12,FThe 50-year-old was initially charged
OL,13,Fwith attempting to murder her
OL,14,Festranged husband by inviting him to
OL,15,Fthe lunch in July 2023, as well as,
OL,16,Fattempting to murder him on three
OL,17,Foccasions around Victoria between
OL,18,FNovember 2021 and September 2022.
OL,20,FBut those charges were dropped ahead
OL,21,Fof the trial beginning in April.
