OL,3,CAustralia's mushroom killer tried to
OL,4,Cpoison husband three times, court hears
OL,6,FOn Friday, a judge lifted a gag order
OL,7,Fon the pre-trial evidence about
OL,8,Fprevious poisoning allegations, which
OL,9,Fher lawyers had wanted to keep secret
OL,10,Fwhile appealing her convictions.
OL,12,FSimon Patterson told the court during
OL,13,Fa pre-trial hearing that he had
OL,14,Fdeclined his estranged wife's lunch
OL,15,Finvitation out of fear.
OL,17,FHe said while he had stopped eating
OL,18,Ffood prepared by his wife, from whom
OL,19,Fhe had been estranged since 2015, he
OL,20,Fnever thought others would be at risk.
