OL,3,CAustralia's mushroom killer tried to
OL,4,Cpoison husband three times, court hears
OL,6,FHe said he suspected his wife had
OL,7,Fdeliberately made him seriously ill
OL,8,Fduring family camping trips with
OL,9,Fdishes including penne bolognese
OL,10,Fpasta, chicken korma curry and a
OL,11,Fvegetable curry wrap.
OL,13,FNo poisons were ever found.
OL,15,FThe court heard Simon Patterson shared
OL,16,Fhis poisoning suspicions with his
OL,17,Fdoctor, who encouraged him to create a
OL,18,Fspreadsheet outlining what he had
OL,19,Featen around the time he became sick.
