OL,3,CAustralia's mushroom killer tried to
OL,4,Cpoison husband three times, court hears
OL,6,FErin Patterson will be sentenced later
OL,7,Fthis month.
OL,9,FShe faces a potential life sentence
OL,10,Ffor each of the murders and 25 years
OL,11,Ffor attempted murder.
OL,13,FThe case has attracted widespread
OL,14,Fnational and international attention.
OL,16,FPatterson's lawyers wanted all the
OL,17,Fevidence that was not relevant to her
OL,18,Ftrial kept secret until an appeals
OL,19,Fcourt decided whether to overturn her
OL,20,Fconvictions.
