OL,3,CAustralia's mushroom killer tried to
OL,4,Cpoison husband three times, court hears
OL,6,FThat was partly due to the
OL,7,Funprecedented media interest in the
OL,8,Fcase.
OL,10,FDefense lawyer Colin Mandy argued that
OL,11,Freporting of the suppressed evidence,
OL,12,Fas well as, references to it in books,
OL,13,Fpodcasts and a planned television mini-
OL,14,Fseries would "leave an indelible
OL,15,Fimpression on the minds of potential
OL,16,Fjurors in the event that there is a
OL,17,Fretrial."
